n"},"id":"936f7c0c-95c2-4e84-823d-847b1c0b606d","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["<em>Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.</em>","The Blip Wi-Fi Weight Scale is an unusual digital <a href=\"/best-bathroom-scales\">bathroom scale</a> that is compatible with both Apple and Android products, though not with third-party apps. Once you have synced it to your account, you can set up online reminders so the scale will issue audible beeps when it&#39;s time for you to weigh in.","This scale can handle up to 10 users (two regular users and eight guests), which is quite a lot in the world of bathroom scales. It can deal with weights as high as 400 pounds. It also recalls your previous weight and can tell you your body mass index (BMI).","One unusual benefit of this scale is that it permits you to track weights and BMI measurements remotely, so if, for example, you have an aging family member and you are worried about that person getting regular meals and staying at a healthy weight, you can keep tabs on that loved one. As long as that individual has Wi-Fi in the home, this scale sends their data to you either online, by email or by smartphone.","This bathroom scale does not measure such things as heart rate or body fat. However, this was a conscious choice by the manufacturer because, in order to measure these things, a scale must send a current through your body as you stand on it. Individuals with pacemakers and pregnant women often are advised to avoid scales that do that because of potential risks to their health.","This scale lets you set goals, uploads data automatically, prepares charts for you and permits data sharing with a doctor, personal trainer or someone else you choose. However, unlike the best bathroom scales, it does not sync with third-party apps, so you can&#39;t pair your smart scale with apps that let you create a custom fitness plan with calorie counting, workout schedules or running routes.","You get a one-year warranty with this scale, along with a product manual, FAQs, email support, data-sharing capabilities and a blog. There is no manufacturer-sponsored community forum where you can discuss health questions or tech problems with people who have the same scale. When it comes to phone support, though, this scale&#39;s company is excellent. Pleasant people answer the phone promptly or call back in a timely manner if you leave a voicemail. They courteously answer any questions you might pose about the Blip Wi-Fi Weight Scale."]},"id":"0e70dbcf-3bee-425c-bfea-5f8e58c249d7","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"799700ca-841f-4214-bf4e-a94241dd03dc","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Blip Wi-Fi Weight Scale fits nicely into weight- and BMI-tracking efforts. However, it does not sync with third-party apps, which prevents you from doing much more than weighing and tracking with this scale."]},"id":"b259af3a-0c33-4078-83f5-b22e08f69d5f","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_60280","url":"/blip-wifi-weight-scale-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"rebecca-spear","url":"/author/rebecca-spear","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Rebecca Spear","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"X8Ccy4LP9pMXtXdurbSshX","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-08-21T22:21:44Z","datePublished":"2014-08-21T22:21:44Z","name":"Blip Wi-Fi Weight Scale","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"rating":87,"verdict":"This digital bathroom scale keeps you weighing in regularly with its remin